item.title: SAMM PDF
item.description: This is a long awaited moment since the release of SAMM version 2. The community asked for it so we’ve created a PDF version of the model. View the SAMM PDF here . If you have any feedback on this, please use our Slack channel or the Discussions on GitHub.
